isplay player controls (like a play button or volume control) within a dark or light control bar'=>'该参数表示的嵌入式播放器是否会显示暗或亮的播放控件（如播放键或音量控制）','YouTube video player with advanced settings'=>'YouTube视频播放器的高级设置','Vimeo'=>'Vimeo','Url of Vimeo page with video'=>'Vimeo视频页面链接','Vimeo video'=>'Vimeo视频','Screenr'=>'Screenr','Audio'=>'音频','File'=>'文件','Audio file url. Supported formats: mp3, ogg'=>'音频文件链接。支持格式：mp3,ogg','Player width. You can specify width in percents and player will be responsive. Example values: <b%value>200px</b>, <b%value>100&#37;</b>'=>'播放器宽度。你可以使用百分比或指定宽度。例如：<b%value>200px</b>, <b%value>100&#37;</b>','Play file automatically when page is loaded'=>'页面加载时自动播放文件。','Repeat when playback is ended'=>'当播放结束重复播放。','ID'=>'ID','URL'=>'网址','Expand'=>'展开','YouTube advanced'=>'高级 YouTube','Learn more'=>'了解更多','Choose file'=>'选择文件','Insert'=>'插入','Select images'=>'选择图像','Add selected images'=>'添加所选的图像','Please enter a name for new preset'=>'请为新的预设输入名称','New preset'=>'新的预设','This shortcode doesn\'t work in live preview. Please insert it into editor and preview on the site.'=>'简码不能在实时预览。请把它插入到编辑器然后再网站上预览。','All'=>'全部','Content'=>'内容','Box'=>'框符','Media'=>'媒体','Gallery'=>'相册','Data'=>'数据','Other'=>'其它','None'=>'无','Solid'=>'立体','Dotted'=>'虚线','Dashed'=>'虚线（破折号）','Double'=>'双虚线','Groove'=>'凹槽','Ridge'=>'棱','Heading'=>'打头标题','Default'=>'默认','Style'=>'风格','Choose style for this heading'=>'为打头标题选择风格','Size'=>'尺寸','Select heading size (pixels)'=>'设置标题的尺寸（pixels）','Left'=>'左','Center'=>'中','Right'=>'右','Align'=>'对齐方式','Heading text alignment'=>'打头文本的对齐方式','Class'=>'样式','Heading text'=>'标题文字','Styled heading'=>'标题风格','Tabs'=>'标签选项卡','Choose style for this tabs'=>'选择选项卡的风格','Active tab'=>'活动标签','Select which tab is open by default'=>'选择哪个标签是默认打开的','Vertical'=>'垂直','Tabs container'=>'选项卡','Extra CSS class'=>'额外的CSS','Tab'=>'单一选项卡','Google map'=>'Google 地图','General settings'=>'常规设置','Dailymotion'=>'Dailymotion','Dailymotion video'=>'Dailymotion视频','Default value'=>'默认值','Padding'=>'