%2$s %3$s - 显示从9:00到18:00的内容%4$s-显示从9:00到13:00以及从14:00到18:00的内容 %5$s -以分钟为单位的示例（每天45分钟可见内容）%6$s -以秒为例','Post type of the post you want to display the data from'=>'要显示数据的文章的文章类型','Private note for post authors. Any content wrapped with this shortcode will only be visible to post authors (users with publish_posts capability).'=>'文章作者的个人注释。用此简码包装的所有内容仅对文章作者（具有publish_posts功能的用户）可见。','Recent media'=>'最近的媒体','Scroll – tab bar will be scrollable horizontally'=>'滚动-标签栏将可水平滚动','Select link alignment'=>'选择链接对齐方式','Select the style for more/less link'=>'选择更多/更少链接的样式','Set this option to No to disable lightbox on mobile devices (≤768px)'=>'将此选项设置为“否”可禁用移动设备上的灯箱（≤768px）','Set this option to Yes to display image captions.'=>'将此选项设置为“是”以显示图像标题。','Sets the time interval between automatic slide transitions, in seconds. Set to 0 to disable autoplay.'=>'设置自动幻灯片切换之间的时间间隔（以秒为单位）。设置为0以禁用自动播放。','Shortcodes Ultimate is not activated, because it requires PHP version %1$s (or higher). You have version %2$s.'=>'未激活Shortcodes Ultimate，因为它需要PHP版本%1$s（或更高版本）。您有版本 %2$s。','Shortcodes Ultimate is not activated, because it requires WordPress version %1$s (or higher). You have version %2$s.'=>'未激活Shortcodes Ultimate，因为它需要WordPress版本%1$s（或更高版本）。您有版本%2$s。','Show more'=>'显示更多','Show related videos'=>'显示相关视频','Show related videos at the end of the video'=>'在视频末尾显示相关视频','Show video info'=>'显示视频信息','Slow'=>'慢速','Start the playback of the video automatically after the player load. May not work on some mobile OS versions'=>'播放器加载后自动开始播放视频。可能不适用于某些移动手机系统版本','Styled table from CSV file'=>'CSV文件中的样式表','Subtitles'=>'字幕','Switch to Image Carousel'=>'切换到图像轮播','Text with icon'=>'带图标的文字','The download attribute specifies that the button URL will be downloaded when a user clicks on the button. The value of the attribute will be the name of the downloaded file.'=>'下载属性指定当用户单击按钮时将下载的网址。该属性的值将是下载文件的名称。','There is a much better shortcode for your images. Have you already tried the Image Carousel? It can create both sliders and carousels.'=>'有一个更好的图像简码。您是否已经尝试过图像轮播？它可以创建滑块和轮播。','Thickness of a margin (in pixels)'=>'外边距的厚度（以像素为单位）','This option adds links to carousel slides.'=>'该选项将添加到轮播幻灯片的链接。','This option control slides transition speed.'=>'此选项控制滑动过渡速度。','This option controls how shortcode will look and function on mobile devices.'=>'此选项控制简码在移动设备上的外观和功能。','This option controls how slide links will be opened.'=>'此选项控制如何打开幻灯片链接。','This option controls how the gallery will be aligned within a page. Left, Right, and Center options require Max Width to be set. Full option requires page template with no sidebar.'=>'此选项控制画廊在页面中的对齐方式。 “左”，“右”和“中心”选项需要设置“最大宽度”。完全选项要求页面模板没有侧边栏。','This option controls the size of carousel slide images. This option only affects image quality, not the actual slide size.'=>'此选项控制轮播幻灯片图像的大小。此选项仅影响图像质量，而不影响实际的幻灯片大小。','This option defines which images will be shown in the gallery. Images can be selected manually from media library or fetched automatically from post featured images, or even filtered by a taxonomy.'=>'此选项定义将在图库中显示哪些图像。可以从媒体库中手动选择图像，也可以从文章精选图片中自动获取，甚至可以通过分类进行筛选。','This parameter controls whether videos play inline or fullscreen in an HTML5 player on iOS'=>'此参数控制视频是在iOS的HTML5播放器中以嵌入播放还是全屏播放','You are editing advanced settings. Do NOT modify anything in here unless you know what you are doing.'=>'正在编辑高级设置。除非您知道自己在做什么，否则请不要在此处进行任何修改。','You can specify custom post ID. Post slug is also allowed. Leave this field empty to use ID of the current post. Current post ID may not work in Live Preview mode'=>'您可以指定自定义文章ID。文章别名也允许。将此字段留空以使用当前文章的ID。当前文章ID在实时预览模式下可能不起作用','Use this field to add custom links to slides used with Slider, Carousel and Custom Gallery shortcodes'=>'使用此字段可将自定义链接添加到与滑块，轮播和自定义画廊简码一起使用的幻灯片','Use template file name (with optional .php extension). If you need to use templates from theme sub-folder, use relative path. Example values: %1$s, %2$s, %3$s'=>'使用模板文件名（带有可选的.php扩展名）。 如果您需要使用主题子文件夹中的模板，请使用相对路径。 值示例：%1$s, %2$s, %3$s','Underlined'=>'下划线','Title attribute'=>'标题属性','This text block can be expanded'=>'此文本块可以展开','This prefix will be used in shortcode names. For example: set <code>MY_</code> prefix and shortcodes will look like <code>[MY_button]</code>. Please note that this setting does not change shortcodes that have been inserted earlier. Change this setting very carefully.'=>'此前缀将用于简码名称。 例如：设置<code>MY_</code>前缀，简码将看起来像<code>[MY_button]</code>。 请注意，此设置不会更改之前插入的简码。小心更改此设置。','This parameter specifies whether the video will automatically start to play when the player loads. Please note, in modern browsers autoplay option only works with the mute option enabled'=>'此参数指定播放器加载时视频是否将自动开始播放。 请注意，在现代浏览器中，自动播放选项仅在启用了静音选项的情况下有效','This option hides all deprecated shortcodes from the Insert Shortcode window and at the Available Shortcodes page. Hidden shortcodes will continue to work.'=>'此选项在“插入简码”窗口和“可用简码”页面中隐藏所有不推荐使用的简码。 隐藏的简码将继续起作用。','This option enables outline when carousel gets focus. The outline improves keyboard navigation.'=>'当轮播获得焦点时，此选项启用轮廓。 该轮廓改善了键盘导航。','This option control the number of columns used in the carousel.'=>'此选项控制轮播中使用的列数。','This option control carousel slides appearance.'=>'此选项控制轮播幻灯片的外观。','This option control carousel controls appearance.'=>'此选项控制轮播控制外观。','This option allows you to hide less link, when the text block has been expanded'=>'扩展文本块后，此选项可让您隐藏较少的链接','This option allows you to enable shortcodes in places where they are disabled by default'=>'此选项使您可以在“默认情况下禁用简码”的位置启用简码','This option allows to enable/disable image cropping and crop aspect ratio.'=>'此选项允许启用/禁用图像裁剪和裁剪纵横比。','This content will be available only for non-logged visitors'=>'此内容仅对未登录的访问者可用','You can apply custom filter to the retrieved value. Enter here function name. Your function must accept one argument and return modified value. Name of your function must include word <b>filter</b>. Example function: '=>'您可以将自定义过滤器应用于检索到的值。 在此处输入函数名称。 您的函数必须接受一个参数并返回修改后的值。 函数名称必须包含单词<b>filter</b>。 示例功能：','Years'=>'年','Text widgets'=>'文本小工具','Text alignment'=>'文本对齐','Testimonial'=>'感言','Supported blocks'=>'支持的区块','Styled table'=>'样式表','Splash screen'=>'闪屏','Spacing'=>'间距','Slides style'=>'幻灯片样式','Slide link (added in media editor)'=>'幻灯片链接（在媒体编辑器中添加）','Slide link'=>'幻灯片链接','Show videos info (title/author) on the start screen'=>'在开始屏幕上显示视频信息（标题/作者）','Show logo'=>'显示 logo','Show less'=>'显示较少','Setting this parameter to YES will block the player from tracking any playback session data. Will have the same effect as enabling a Do Not Track header in your browser'=>'将此参数设置为YES将阻止播放器跟踪任何播放会话数据。 与在浏览器中启用“不跟踪”标头具有相同的效果','Sets maximum width of the carousel container. CSS uints are allowed.'=>'设置轮播容器的最大宽度。 允许使用CSS单位。','Set the field delimiter (one character only)'=>'设置字段定界符（仅一个字符）','Rel attribute'=>'Rel 属性','Rel'=>'Rel','Quality'=>'质量','please specify the data'=>'请指定数据','please specify template name'=>'请指定模板名称','Plays inline'=>'嵌入播放','Photo panel'=>'照片面板','Panel'=>'面板','NOT IN - posts that is does not have any of selected terms'=>'NOT IN-没有任何选定字词的文章','Mute'=>'静音','More text'=>'更多文字','Mute the player'=>'使播放器静音','More icon'=>'更多图标','Months'=>'月','Meta data'=>'元数据','Member'=>'会员','Max width'=>'最大宽度','Link tab to any webpage. Use full URL to turn the tab title into link'=>'链接选项卡到任何网页。 使用完整的URL将标签标题变为链接','Link style'=>'链接样式','Link align'=>'链接对齐','Lightbox content'=>'灯箱内容','Less text'=>'较少文字','Last used settings'=>'上次使用的设置','invalid URL'=>'无效网址','invalid delimiter'=>'无效的分隔符','Insert here URL or CSS selector. Use URL for Iframe and Image content types. Use CSS selector for Inline content type.<br />Example values:<br /><b%value>http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XXXXXXXXX</b> - YouTube video (iframe)<br /><b%value>http://example.com/wp-content/uploads/image.jpg</b> - uploaded image (image)<br /><b%value>http://example.com/</b> - any web page (iframe)<br /><b%value>#my-custom-popup</b> - any HTML content (inline)'=>'在此处插入URL或CSS选择器。 将网址用于iframe和图片内容类型。 将CSS选择器用于Inline 内容类型。<br />值示例:<br /><b%value>http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XXXXXXXXX</b> - YouTube 视频 (iframe)<br /><b%value>http://example.com/wp-content/uploads/image.jpg</b> - 已上传的图像 (图像)<br /><b%value>http://example.com/</b> - 任何网页 (iframe)<br /><b%value>#my-custom-popup</b> - 任何HTML内容(inline)','Indent'=>'缩进','In this field you can write your custom CSS code for shortcodes. These styles will have higher priority compared to original styles of shortcodes. You can use variables in your CSS code. These variables will be replaced by respective values.'=>'在此字段中，您可以为简码编写自定义CSS代码。 与原始的简码样式相比，这些样式将具有更高的优先级。 您可以在CSS代码中使用变量。 这些变量将被相应的值替换。','In this field you can type the text which will be shown if content is not visible at the current moment'=>'在此字段中，如果内容在当前不可见，您可以输入将显示的文本','In this field you can specify the year or years in which the content will be visible. %1$s %2$s %3$s - show content only in 2014 %4$s - show content from 2014 to 2016 %5$s - show content in 2014, 2018 and from 2020 to 2022'=>'在此字段中，您可以指定显示内容的年份。 %1$s %2$s %3$s-仅显示2014年的内容%4$s -显示2014年至2016年的内容 %5$s -显示2014年，2018年以及2020年至2022年的内容','In this field you can specify the month or months in which the content will be visible. %1$s %2$s %3$s - show content only in January %4$s - show content from February to June %5$s - show content in January, March and from May to July'=>'在此字段中，您可以指定显示内容的月份。%1$s %2$s %3$s-仅在1月显示内容%4$s-2月至6月显示内容%5$s-1月，3月和5月至7月显示内容','Image carousel'=>'图像轮播','Icon panel'=>'图标面板','HTML color of the foreground of controls elements'=>'控件元素前景的HTML颜色','HTML color of the controls elements\' highlights'=>'控件元素高亮的HTML颜色','Hover me to open tooltip'=>'悬停以打开工具提示','Hit enter to select highlighted shortcode, while searching'=>'在搜索时，按回车键选择高亮的简码','Hide less link'=>'隐藏较少的链接','Hide deprecated shortcodes'=>'隐藏不推荐使用的简码','Here you can specify wmode value for the embed URL.<br>Example values: %1$s, %2$s'=>'在这里，您可以为嵌入的URL指定wmode值。<br>示例值：%1$s, %2$s','Here you can add value for the title attribute'=>'在这里您可以为title属性添加值','Here you can add value for the rel attribute.<br>Example values: <b%value>nofollow</b>, <b%value>lightbox</b>'=>'在这里，您可以为rel属性添加值。<br>值示例: <b%value>nofollow</b>, <b%value>lightbox</b>','Height of the divider (in pixels)'=>'分隔线的高度（以像素为单位）','Height for collapsed state (in pixels)'=>'折叠状态的高度（以像素为单位）','Full'=>'全部','Fixed layout'=>'固定布局','Examples (click to set)'=>'示例（单击设置）','Enter here comma-separated list of author\'s IDs. Example: 1,7,18'=>'在此处输入英文逗号分隔的作者ID列表。 示例：1,7,18','Enable to use alternative background color for even rows'=>'启用对偶数行使用替代背景色','Enable this option if you face any problems with formatting of nested shortcodes.'=>'如果您在嵌套简码格式方面遇到任何问题，请启用此选项。','Enable this option if you don\'t want the inserted shortcode to contain any settings that were not changed by you. As a result, inserted shortcodes will be much shorter.'=>'如果您不希望插入的简码包含您未更改的任何设置，请启用此选项。 因此，插入的简码将短得多。','Enable shortcodes in'=>'启用简码在','Do not crop images'=>'不裁剪图像','Divider color'=>'分隔线颜色','Display header'=>'显示页头','Display first row as table header'=>'显示第一行作为表格标题','Did you know that you need to wrap single tabs with [tabs] shortcode?'=>'您是否知道需要用[tabs]简码包装单个选项卡？','Did you know that you can wrap multiple spoilers with [accordion] shortcode to create accordion effect?'=>'您知道吗，您可以用[accordion]简码包装多个spoiler来创建手风琴效果？','Delimiter'=>'定界符','Defines list indent size (in pixels). Negative numbers are also allowed'=>'定义列表缩进大小（以像素为单位）。 也可以使用负数','Dark'=>'暗黑','Customizable image gallery (slider and carousel)'=>'可自定义的图片库（滑块和轮播）','Custom value for the ID attribute'=>'ID属性的自定义值','Crop images'=>'裁切图像','Columns'=>'栏','Close (Esc)'=>'关闭（Esc）','Click here to open lightbox'=>'单击此处打开灯箱','Choose style for this divider'=>'选择此分隔线的样式','By default, the content of this shortcode will be visible all the time. By using fields below, you can add some limitations. For example, if you type 1-5 in the Days of the week field, content will be only shown from Monday to Friday. Using the same principles, you can limit content visibility from years to seconds.'=>'默认情况下，此简码的内容将始终可见。 通过使用下面的字段，您可以添加一些限制。 例如，如果您在“星期几”字段中键入1-5，则仅在星期一至星期五显示内容。同理，您可以将内容可见性从几年限制到几秒钟。','Alternative text'=>'替换文字','Alternate row color'=>'交替行颜色','Alignment'=>'对齐','Align tabs vertically'=>'垂直对齐选项卡','Advanced QR code generator'=>'高级QR码生成器','Adjust the top and bottom margins of this divider (in pixels)'=>'调整此分隔线的上下外边距（以像素为单位）','Adjust the shadow for content box'=>'调整内容框的阴影','Adds spacing between carousel columns.'=>'在轮播栏之间增加间距。','Add horizontal scrollbar if table width larger than page width'=>'如果表格宽度大于页面宽度，则添加水平滚动条','Add an icon to the more link'=>'在更多链接中添加图标','Add an icon to the less link'=>'在更少链接中添加图标','Adaptive'=>'自适应','A value for the title attribute of the link'=>'标题链接属性的值','A value for the rel attribute of the link'=>'rel链接属性的值','A user must have this capability to be able to use the "Insert Shortcode" button. Do not change this value if you do not understand its meaning as this may lower the plugin security.'=>'用户必须具有此权限才能使用“插入简码”按钮。 如果您不了解其含义，请勿更改此值，因为这可能会降低插件的安全性。','%1$s of %2$s'=>'第%1$s 张，共 %2$s张','Fixed width table cells'=>'定宽单元格','Zoom sets the initial zoom level of the map. Accepted values range from 1 (the whole world) to 21 (individual buildings). Use 0 (zero) to set zoom level depending on displayed object (automatic)'=>'缩放设置地图的初始缩放级别。 可接受的值范围是1（整个世界）到21（单个建筑物）。 使用0（零）设置缩放级别，具体取决于显示的对象（自动）','Zoom'=>'缩放','Immediate'=>'即时','Captions'=>'标题','Pro Tip'=>'专家提示','Offset'=>'偏移','Specify offset to start posts loop not from first post'=>'指定开始文章循环的偏移量，而不是从第一篇文章开始','Time'=>'时间','Days of the week'=>'一周中的日子','Days of the month'=>'一个月中的天数','In this field you can specify one or more days of the week. Every week at these days the content of shortcode will be visible. %1$s 0 - Sunday %2$s 1 - Monday %3$s 2 - Tuesday %4$s 3 - Wednesday %5$s 4 - Thursday %6$s 5 - Friday %7$s 6 - Saturday %8$s %9$s %10$s - show content from Monday to Friday %11$s - show content only at Sunday %12$s - show content at Sunday and from Wednesday to Friday'=>'在此字段中，您可以指定一周中的一或几天。 每周中这些天都会看到简码的内容。 %1$s 0-星期日 %2$s 1-星期一%3$s 2-星期二%4$s 3-星期三%5$s 4-星期四%6$s 5-星期五%7$s 6-星期六%8$s %9$s %10$s-从星期一至星期五显示内容 %11$s-仅在星期日显示内容 %12$s -在星期日以及从星期三至星期五显示的内容','In this field you can specify one or more days of the month. Every month at these days the content of shortcode will be visible. %1$s %2$s %3$s - show content only at first day of month %4$s - show content from 1th to 5th %5$s - show content from 10th to 15th and from 20th to 25th'=>'在此字段中，您可以指定一个月中的一天或几天。每个月里这些天都会显示简码的内容。 %1$s %2$s %3$s-仅在每月的第一天显示内容%4$s -显示1日至5日的内容%5$s-显示10日至15日以及20日至25日的内容','Enter the text for more link'=>'输入“更多链接”的文字','Enter the text for less link'=>'输入“更少链接”的文字','Controls style'=>'控制方式','Expandable text block'=>'可扩展文本区块','Fluid'=>'易变','Fluid buttons has 100% width'=>'易变按钮有100％的宽度','Radius of button corners. Auto-radius calculation based on button size'=>'按钮圆角半径。根据按钮大小自动计算半径。','Wrapper'=>'包裹','Wrap the dummy text with a div container'=>'用div容器包装虚拟文本','Landscape'=>'横向','Outline on focus'=>'聚焦时轮廓','Set this option to Yes to ignore the columns parameter and display a single column on mobile devices.'=>'将此选项设置为“是”可忽略栏参数，并在移动设备上显示单栏。','Did you know that you need to wrap columns with [row] shortcode?'=>'您是否知道您需要使用[row]简码包装栏？','Select column width. This width will be calculated depend page width'=>'选择栏的宽度。此宽度将根据页面宽度进行计算','Row for flexible columns'=>'灵活栏的行','Column content'=>'栏内容','Column'=>'栏','Required user capability'=>'所需的用户权限','Tooltip'=>'工具提示','Tooltip window with custom content'=>'带有自定义内容的工具提示窗口','Tooltip title'=>'工具提示标题','Tooltip position'=>'工具提示位置','Tooltip content'=>'工具提示内容','This parameter determines what HTML tag will be used for animation wrapper. Turn this option to YES and animated element will be wrapped in SPAN instead of DIV. Useful for inline animations, like buttons'=>'此参数决定将哪个HTML标记用于动画包装。 选项设置为YES，动画元素将包装在SPAN中，而不是DIV中。 对于内嵌动画（如按钮）很有用','You can use unique anchor for this tab to access it with hash in page url. For example: use <b%value>Hello</b> and then navigate to url like http://example.com/page-url#Hello. This tab will be activated and scrolled in'=>'您可以对此标签使用唯一锚点，可访问带hash的页面URL。 例如：使用<b%value>Hello</b>，然后导航至类似 http://example.com/page-url#Hello的网址。 此选项卡将被激活并滚动','Flexible and responsive columns'=>'灵活和自适应式栏','Is this column centered on the page'=>'这一栏是否在页面上居中','Ghost'=>'幽灵','A brief description of the embedded content (used by screenreaders)'=>'嵌入式内容的简要说明（供屏幕阅读器使用）','Margin'=>'外边距','Bottom margin (pixels)'=>'底外边距(pixels)','Field'=>'字段','Note'=>'注释','WMode'=>'WMode','Example values'=>'示例值','Select taxonomy and it\'s terms.<br>You can select multiple terms with Ctrl (Cmd) key'=>'选择分类和它的条件。您可以选择多个条件用Ctrl（CMD）键','Select categories to retrieve posts from.<br>You can select multiple categories with Ctrl (Cmd) key'=>'选择要从中检索文章的分类。搜寻您可以选择多个分类，按Ctrl（CMD）键。','Click the button above and select images.<br>You can select multimple images with Ctrl (Cmd) key'=>'点击上面的按钮，并选择图像。您可以选择多个图像，按Ctrl（CMD）键','You can use unique anchor for this spoiler to access it with hash in page url. For example: type here <b%value>Hello</b> and then use url like http://example.com/page-url#Hello. This spoiler will be open and scrolled in'=>'您可以使用独特的锚点这个spoiler，在页面的URL访问它。例如：在这里输入<b%value>你好</ b>和使用的URL如http://example.com/page-url#你好。这spoiler会打开、滚动。','Enabled'=>'开启','Vladimir Anokhin'=>'Vladimir Anokhin','Rate plugin'=>'利率插件','Remind me later'=>'稍后提醒我','Click to return to the shortcodes list'=>'点击返回到简码列表','All shortcodes'=>'全部简码','Preview'=>'预览','Add-ons'=>'附加组件','Documentation'=>'说明文档','Shortcodes Ultimate'=>'终极简码','WordPress.org'=>'WordPress.org','https://getshortcodes.com/'=>'https://getshortcodes.com/','More information'=>'更多信息','Will be replaced with'=>'将被替换为','the URL of the site home page'=>'网站首页的URL','the URL of the directory of the plugin'=>'插件目录的URL','the URL of the directory of the current theme'=>'当前主题目录的URL','Thank you!'=>'谢谢！','Plugin website'=>'插件网站','Hello'=>'您好','Available variables'=>'可用变量','Help article'=>'帮助文章','Shortcode'=>'简码','Variable'=>'变量','Plugin settings overview'=>'插件设置概述','Open %s file to see default styles'=>'打开%s文件以查看默认样式','How to use Custom CSS editor'=>'如何使用自定义CSS编辑器','Getting started'=>'开始体验吧','Dismiss'=>'忽略','Details & Pricing'=>'详情和价格','with trailing slash'=>'带有斜杠/','A comprehensive collection of visual components for WordPress'=>'WordPress的视觉组件的所有集合']];